name: Lucus
string:
Hey <player>…
Isn't that a
glacier? Cool!
It's my first
time to see one!
Oh! you can use
it to convert
the shipping
storage into a
refrigerator!
You can keep the
vegetables for a
long time now.
Do you have a
garbage disposal
at home? That
could be a
problem. If the
vegetables stay
fresh, you won't
have rotten
vegetables to
make fertilizer.
Do you want to
convert the
storage into a
refrigerator?
 Yes          No<ask>

name: Lucus
string:
Alright! I'll
work on it right
away. I'll show
you how talented
I am!

name: Lucus
string:
OK… Ask me
if you change
your mind.
